               <msContents>
                  <summary>Mystagogia, ትምህርተ፡ ኅቡዓት፡, incomplete at beginning and end; Prayer of the Covenant, ጸሎተ፡ ኪዳን፡, incomplete at the beginning; Anaphora of Our Lord, ቅዳሴ፡ እግዚእ፡; Prayer of Supplication, በእንተ፡ ቅድሳት፡ ሰላማዊት፡; Hymns after communion; Hymn to Saint George, “Hail to you, Saint George,” በኀከ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡</summary>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="6v" facs="001">Fols 1r–6v</locus><title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2444Temher">Tǝmhǝrta
                                                  ḫǝbuʾāt</title><note>incomplete at the beginning</note></msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="7r" to="16v" facs="007">Fols 7r–16v</locus><title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2260salota">Ṣalota kidān</title><note>incomplete at the beginning</note></msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3"><locus from="16v" to="22v" facs="017">Fols 16v–22v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1100Anapho">ʾAkkʷateta qʷǝrbān
                                                  za-ʾǝgziʾǝna ʾIyasus Krǝstos</title></msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4"><locus from="23r" to="25v" facs="023">Fols 23r–25v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2961RepCh242">Hymn to St
                                                  George</title>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i5"><locus from="25v" to="26r" facs="026">Fols 25v–26r</locus>
                  <title>Hymns after communion</title>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">ቅዱስ፡ ስሉስ፡ ዘኢይትነገር፡ ኀበኒ፡ ከመ፡ እንሳዕ፡ ለሕይወት፡...</incipit>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i6">
                  <locus from="26r" to="27v" facs="026">Fols 26r–27v</locus>
                    <title>Hymn to Saint George, “Hail to you, Saint George” </title>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                      በኀከ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ በኀከ፡ ወሬዛ፡ ኃያል፡
                      ከመ፡ አንበሳ፡ ውኩል፡
                      እምከመ፡ ተነፍሐ፡ ቀርነ፡ ኢዮቤል፡
                      ዕንቋ፡ ይበል፡ ለመአዛ፡ ቀትል፡ ፈረስከ፡ ይብል።
                    </incipit>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
